      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROSCOE CONKLIN (1) steps out for the first time at this course. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 6 lengths (19.72) at Bulli. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Worth another chance. NITRO VENOM (8) had second look this course and distance latest and improved on his time, finishing a 3 length third in 20.15. Bold showing expected again. SILENT ACCORD (7) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 6 lengths into third (19.97) at this track in a Grade 5 over 350m. Expected to be in this for a long way. MADE BY MIA (2) did a good job to finish third last time out over 365m at Nowra (21.17) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
